  "body": "if you provide:\n\n```\nstatic_configs:\n  - files:\n    - /path/to/files*.json\n```\n\nin prometheus.yml (which is wrong, it should be `file_sd_configs` instead of `static_configs`) at least promtool complains about:\n`FAILED: unknown fields in target_group: files`\n\nThis error is quite misleading and makes it harder to locate the actual problem.\n\nMy short digging into the topic revealed that something might be [calling checkOverflow with a wrongly labeled context](https://github.com/prometheus/prometheus/blob/master/config/config.go#L226), but I haven't digged too far, I must admit.\n",
